---
title: All-American Pork & Roast Pumpkin Slaw with Mayonnaise & Parsley
description: Tonight is a celebration in a bowl, so get your knives and forks at the ready because once this dish hits the table it’s party time. Let your tastebuds dance away to the showstopping pumpkin dressed in a zesty slaw. The real fun begins when you take a bite of tender spiced pork, seared, sliced and drizzled in mayo.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
